WEBVTT

00:01.201 --> 00:03.502
♪

00:03.504 --> 00:07.706
<i>(muffled conversation)</i>

00:07.708 --> 00:11.176
<i>♪ (mounting tension)</i>

00:11.178 --> 00:13.212
♪

00:13.214 --> 00:17.750
(muffled conversation continues)

00:17.752 --> 00:21.220
♪

00:21.222 --> 00:24.656
Whatever they decide, apple
bloom, we'll be here for you.

00:24.658 --> 00:28.327
Even though it could
change everything for you!

00:28.329 --> 00:30.195
<i>Forever! And ever!</i>

00:31.064 --> 00:32.364
<i>(rattling)</i>

00:32.366 --> 00:36.335
<i>(creak)</i>

00:38.605 --> 00:44.676
<i>♪ (military snare drum)</i>

00:48.281 --> 00:49.715
So.

00:49.717 --> 00:52.418
We here have decided...

00:55.588 --> 00:57.589
That you're old enough
to stay home alone

00:57.591 --> 01:00.793
And take care of the chores
yourself for the afternoon.

01:00.795 --> 01:02.061
<i>(happy gasp)</i>

01:05.565 --> 01:07.266
I accept your decision.

01:07.268 --> 01:13.272
<i>♪ (snare drum)</i>

01:13.274 --> 01:14.473
<i>(happy shouts)</i>

01:14.475 --> 01:16.141
I'm staying home alone!
Whoo hoo!

01:20.346 --> 01:23.182
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:23.184 --> 01:25.184
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

01:25.186 --> 01:26.218
<i>♪ (upbeat)</i>

01:26.220 --> 01:28.387
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

01:28.389 --> 01:30.556
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

01:30.558 --> 01:32.491
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

01:32.493 --> 01:34.693
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

01:34.695 --> 01:35.861
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

01:35.863 --> 01:37.129
<i>♪ tons of fun.</i>

01:37.131 --> 01:38.163
<i>♪ a beautiful heart</i>

01:38.165 --> 01:39.231
<i>♪ faithful and strong</i>

01:39.233 --> 01:40.332
<i>♪ sharing kindness</i>

01:40.334 --> 01:43.268
<i>♪ and magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete ♪</i>

01:43.270 --> 01:45.404
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

01:45.406 --> 01:48.474
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:48.476 --> 01:50.876
♪

01:57.150 --> 02:00.586
<i>♪ (banjo)</i>

02:00.588 --> 02:13.499
<i>♪</i>

02:13.501 --> 02:15.134
Staying home alone.

02:15.136 --> 02:17.603
By myself! On my own!

02:17.605 --> 02:18.704
<i>(crash)</i>

02:18.706 --> 02:20.439
<i>(falling whistle)</i>

02:23.543 --> 02:25.444
I can't believe I'm
really doing it!

02:25.446 --> 02:27.913
Now, hey there, filly.
I know you're excited.

02:27.915 --> 02:31.150
But bein' the only pony here to
take care of the day's chores

02:31.152 --> 02:32.618
Is a big responsibility.

02:32.620 --> 02:35.787
And it means everything
to me that ya'll think

02:35.789 --> 02:37.756
I'm grown up enough
to handle it.

02:37.758 --> 02:39.725
I won't let you down!

02:39.727 --> 02:43.295
Well, if'n I'm gonna make
my train, I best to be off.

02:43.297 --> 02:46.265
When great-aunt pine apple
says a pony's gots to arrive

02:46.267 --> 02:49.301
By a certain time, you
better be there!

02:49.303 --> 02:51.803
You be sure and take
care now, apple bloom.

02:53.773 --> 02:55.741
Y'all take care as well.

02:55.743 --> 02:58.911
I don't know which of your
delivery routes is tougher.

02:58.913 --> 03:01.914
<i>You're each headed to a</i>
<i>mighty hard-to-reach town.</i>

03:01.916 --> 03:03.949
Yup.

03:03.951 --> 03:07.586
That's the only reason I
agreed to let apple bloom

03:07.588 --> 03:08.687
<i>Stay behind alone.</i>

03:08.689 --> 03:09.922
It is?

03:09.924 --> 03:12.724
Oh, I didn't mean it
like that, sugar cube.

03:12.726 --> 03:16.528
It's just, I take my job as
your big sister real serious.

03:16.530 --> 03:19.264
Which is why I spent
all night making this.

03:20.567 --> 03:21.833
What is it?

03:21.835 --> 03:23.869
Just a little list
of helpful reminders.

03:23.871 --> 03:25.737
"there's some soup for
you in the fridge."

03:25.739 --> 03:27.773
"be sure not to heat
it up too much."

03:27.775 --> 03:29.975
"if its hot, blow on
it to cool it off."

03:29.977 --> 03:33.779
"if you gulp, you
could get hiccups."

03:33.781 --> 03:35.480
You don't have to
worry about me.

03:35.482 --> 03:37.482
I can take of myself
and the chores.

03:37.484 --> 03:38.917
I'm ready for this!

03:38.919 --> 03:41.553
(sigh) I guess you are.

03:41.555 --> 03:43.622
I'm just not so sure I am.

03:43.624 --> 03:46.925
But you trust me and believe I'm
grown up enough to handle this,

03:46.927 --> 03:48.393
Right?

03:50.763 --> 03:52.564
(sigh) right.

03:52.566 --> 03:53.732
Ok, then.

03:53.734 --> 03:54.866
Good luck, little sis.

03:54.868 --> 03:57.236
(fast) ok great! See
you soon. Bye!

03:57.238 --> 04:03.475
♪

04:03.477 --> 04:06.745
<i>All at once: Goodbye! So</i>
<i>long!See ya! Bye now!</i>

04:06.747 --> 04:11.383
♪

04:11.385 --> 04:16.321
<i>♪ (rising violins)</i>

04:16.323 --> 04:16.989
Woo-hoo!

04:16.991 --> 04:18.257
I'm alone!

04:18.259 --> 04:19.358
At home!

04:19.360 --> 04:20.726
I'm home alone!

04:20.728 --> 04:22.561
This is going to be so awesome!

04:22.563 --> 04:24.263
♪

04:30.470 --> 04:31.436
<i>(chattering)</i>

04:35.375 --> 04:36.742
<i>(thud)</i>

04:36.744 --> 04:38.410
Heh heh.

04:38.412 --> 04:39.911
<i>Sorry, big mac.</i>

04:39.913 --> 04:42.381
I was just frettin' a
bit about apple bloom.

04:42.383 --> 04:44.383
You think she's gonna
be ok on her own?

04:44.385 --> 04:45.984
Yup.

04:45.986 --> 04:47.986
I just keep on thinking
of things I forgot

04:47.988 --> 04:52.391
Like, I didn't write down that
if she wants to get a spoon

04:52.393 --> 04:55.327
Out of the drawer, she needs
to open the drawer first.

04:56.729 --> 04:58.597
I know I'm probably
just being silly.

04:58.599 --> 05:02.501
But I know I'd feel a heap
better if I could just

05:02.503 --> 05:04.002
Check on apple bloom
one last time.

05:07.907 --> 05:09.808
You go on ahead and
make your delivery.

05:09.810 --> 05:12.844
I'm just gonna take quick
peek and then I'll make mine.

05:18.818 --> 05:21.019
<i>Apple bloom: Ok, number 172.</i>

05:21.021 --> 05:23.622
"make sure to pump the bellows
to keep the stove warm."

05:25.358 --> 05:27.459
<i>(whoosh whoosh whoosh)</i>

05:27.461 --> 05:31.029
"make sure the hats and bows
closet is fully stocked."

05:32.932 --> 05:33.965
Check!

05:33.967 --> 05:37.669
That's everything
on applejack's list.

05:37.671 --> 05:41.373
And now that my chores are done,
since there's no one else here,

05:41.375 --> 05:43.375
I get to make all the decisions!

05:43.377 --> 05:45.744
If I want to listen
to music, I can!

05:45.746 --> 05:47.913
If I want to read a book, I can!

05:47.915 --> 05:50.749
If I wanna just stand here in
the kitchen talking to myself,

05:50.751 --> 05:51.883
I can!

05:51.885 --> 05:52.851
Gah!
Apple bloom!

05:52.853 --> 05:53.985
Whoa!

05:53.987 --> 05:54.786
<i>(crash)</i>

05:54.788 --> 05:56.021
<i>(clatter)</i>

05:57.790 --> 06:00.459
(sigh) applejack?

06:00.461 --> 06:02.594
I came back to check on you.

06:02.596 --> 06:04.096
And I am so glad I did!

06:06.866 --> 06:08.667
I never thought about how
dangerous things are

06:08.669 --> 06:10.602
Around here.

06:10.604 --> 06:13.438
Thanks. But I'm
really gonna be ok.

06:13.440 --> 06:14.673
You are now.

06:14.675 --> 06:16.808
Because I'm here,
and I'm staying!

06:16.810 --> 06:18.810
No way am I leaving
my little baby sister

06:18.812 --> 06:20.979
Home alone all by herself!

06:20.981 --> 06:22.414
I'm not a baby!

06:22.416 --> 06:23.949
I can take care of myself.

06:23.951 --> 06:26.084
And what about those pies
you're supposed to deliver?

06:26.086 --> 06:30.789
Pies? Ha. Family's way
more important than pies.

06:30.791 --> 06:32.824
But I'm fine.

06:32.826 --> 06:36.828
And actually, this was
kind of your fault.

06:36.830 --> 06:38.663
I know.

06:38.665 --> 06:40.499
I should never have
left you alone.

06:42.468 --> 06:44.102
But I don't need you
looking after me.

06:44.104 --> 06:46.738
I'm perfectly capable
of staying home alone.

06:46.740 --> 06:47.706
Really!

06:49.942 --> 06:51.410
Just look!

06:51.412 --> 06:53.712
"there's some soup for you
in the fridgerator."

06:53.714 --> 06:55.080
What was that?

06:55.082 --> 06:56.448
Watch me.

06:57.583 --> 06:59.117
<i>(clatter)</i>

06:59.119 --> 06:59.951
<i>(splat)</i>

06:59.953 --> 07:00.852
Whoa!

07:02.188 --> 07:03.989
Oh, no!

07:03.991 --> 07:05.690
This is worse than I thought!

07:05.692 --> 07:07.192
Well, don't worry apple bloom.

07:07.194 --> 07:11.129
I'm here now and I'm not leaving
you home alone ever again.

07:11.131 --> 07:14.866
I'm sticking right
by your side, always!

07:14.868 --> 07:17.936
♪

07:20.173 --> 07:22.841
<i>♪ (banjo)</i>

07:22.843 --> 07:23.875
Apple bloom?

07:24.610 --> 07:25.610
Apple bloom!

07:26.679 --> 07:28.814
Applejack's just
over reactin' a bit.

07:28.816 --> 07:30.515
I'm sure she'll snap out of it.

07:30.517 --> 07:31.983
Whoa!

07:31.985 --> 07:32.851
You need something?

07:32.853 --> 07:37.155
I know you mean well, but I
don't need you watching over me.

07:37.157 --> 07:39.558
I can take care
of things myself.

07:39.560 --> 07:40.926
<i>(laugh)</i>

07:40.928 --> 07:42.160
Look!

07:42.162 --> 07:46.565
♪

07:46.567 --> 07:47.165
Huh?

07:48.601 --> 07:51.703
Hey! Who put pillows
on this rake?

07:51.705 --> 07:53.805
(chuckle) oh, I don't know.

07:53.807 --> 07:55.874
Maybe someone who really
loves her little sister

07:55.876 --> 07:57.742
And doesn't want her
to get an owie?

07:59.779 --> 08:00.812
<i>(growl)</i>

08:02.882 --> 08:05.684
Hey, applejack, watch me buck
these apples on my own

08:05.686 --> 08:07.919
Without anything bad
happening to me.

08:08.654 --> 08:09.821
<i>(grunt)</i>

08:09.823 --> 08:12.891
<i>(rustling)</i>

08:12.893 --> 08:14.125
Huh?

08:20.132 --> 08:21.199
<i>(growl)</i>

08:43.589 --> 08:45.590
Agh! For the love of...!

08:45.592 --> 08:48.560
You've gone and
baby-proofed everything!

08:48.562 --> 08:50.161
(chuckle) yup!

08:50.163 --> 08:52.063
Your big sister
let you down once.

08:52.065 --> 08:54.866
But I promise it won't
ever happen again!

08:54.868 --> 08:57.102
But really, I'm fine.

08:57.104 --> 08:58.870
I can take care of myself.

08:58.872 --> 09:01.006
I don't need you
watching over me.

09:01.008 --> 09:03.141
Aw, that's sweet.

09:03.143 --> 09:05.143
I appreciate you trying
to make me feel better.

09:05.145 --> 09:08.280
But don't worry; I'll
always be here for you!

09:08.282 --> 09:10.081
Always!

09:10.083 --> 09:11.983
<i>(growl turning to a scream)</i>

09:13.319 --> 09:15.020
<i>(sigh)</i>

09:15.022 --> 09:17.856
And that's the reason I asked
y'all to come over quick.

09:17.858 --> 09:19.691
<i>Applejack: Hey, apple bloom,</i>
<i>you need anything?</i>

09:19.693 --> 09:21.159
A snack? A hoof massage?

09:21.161 --> 09:23.194
Maybe a snack while
havin' a hoof massage?

09:23.196 --> 09:24.996
Why that sounds delightful!

09:24.998 --> 09:26.865
No thank you!

09:26.867 --> 09:29.734
Ok, well, you can count
on me being closeby

09:29.736 --> 09:30.902
If'n you need anything.

09:30.904 --> 09:31.703
<i>(slam)</i>

09:31.705 --> 09:32.704
Whew!

09:32.706 --> 09:36.808
If this keeps up, I'm never
going to be able to do anything

09:36.810 --> 09:39.110
Without applejack
hoverin' over me!

09:39.112 --> 09:40.745
Mm hm.

09:40.747 --> 09:42.314
So what can we do?

09:42.316 --> 09:44.950
Hmmm... Uh...

09:51.090 --> 09:52.657
Hang on a sec!

09:52.659 --> 09:53.758
I got it!

09:53.760 --> 09:54.793
What?

09:54.795 --> 09:55.961
The pies!

09:55.963 --> 09:57.762
I'll sneak out
and deliver them!

09:57.764 --> 09:58.964
Granny said they were going

09:58.966 --> 10:01.099
To some incredibly
hard-to-reach town.

10:01.101 --> 10:03.635
If I can do it alone,
that'll show applejack

10:03.637 --> 10:06.071
I don't need somepony
watchin' over me!

10:06.073 --> 10:09.007
Just one problem: Your
sister's gonna come back

10:09.009 --> 10:10.775
And check on you any minute!

10:10.777 --> 10:13.745
Which means you
need an escape plan!

10:13.747 --> 10:15.814
Oooh! And I got
an idea for one.

10:23.656 --> 10:27.158
<i>(snoring)</i>

10:27.160 --> 10:29.794
See? It'll look just like
you're sleeping in bed.

10:29.796 --> 10:31.363
Sweetie and I can take turns.

10:31.365 --> 10:34.265
That way, when one of us gets
tired, the other can take over.

10:34.267 --> 10:35.634
Brilliant, huh?

10:35.636 --> 10:36.935
You know what?

10:36.937 --> 10:38.136
It is!

10:38.138 --> 10:40.005
I got a feelin' this
just might work!

10:41.774 --> 10:44.209
<i>♪ we're gonna make my</i>
<i>sister see ♪</i>

10:44.211 --> 10:46.911
<i>♪ I don't need her</i>
<i>watchin' over me! ♪</i>

10:46.913 --> 10:47.846
Stop!

10:47.848 --> 10:49.114
<i>(hoof sounds)</i>

10:49.116 --> 10:51.316
No time for a song!
Applejack's coming!

10:51.318 --> 10:54.419
If you're going to go, we've
got to get you out of here now!

10:54.421 --> 10:57.022
<i>Cutie mark crusaders!</i>
<i>Let's do it!</i>

11:00.993 --> 11:01.926
Whoa!

11:01.928 --> 11:02.827
<i>(thud)</i>

11:10.436 --> 11:15.106
<i>(clattering wheels)</i>

11:16.809 --> 11:19.010
<i>Everything all right</i>
<i>in there, sugar cube?</i>

11:19.012 --> 11:20.712
Quick! Get in while I hide!

11:26.085 --> 11:27.152
Sweetie, no!

11:27.154 --> 11:28.820
You gotta sleep
like apple bloom!

11:28.822 --> 11:30.255
How does she sleep?

11:30.257 --> 11:33.091
Like she does
everything. With sass!

11:36.363 --> 11:38.963
I guess you must've
been so tuckered out

11:38.965 --> 11:40.965
You sent your friends
home and went to bed.

11:40.967 --> 11:43.768
Then again, you are
a delicate flower.

11:43.770 --> 11:45.970
Sleep tight, apple bloom.

11:45.972 --> 11:48.907
I'll check on you
again in a bit.

11:48.909 --> 11:50.175
<i>(door closes)</i>

11:50.177 --> 11:51.810
<i>(relieved sighs)</i>

11:51.812 --> 11:55.046
Just checking in on you again.

11:55.048 --> 11:56.347
<i>(door closes)</i>

11:58.250 --> 12:00.752
Need anything now?

12:00.754 --> 12:02.487
How about now?

12:02.489 --> 12:04.923
Need another blanket?

12:04.925 --> 12:06.958
Did I hear a cough?

12:06.960 --> 12:08.359
Want a glass of water?

12:08.361 --> 12:11.863
<i>(clock ticking)</i>

12:11.865 --> 12:21.473
<i>(snoring)</i>

12:21.475 --> 12:22.907
<i>(door opens)</i>

12:22.909 --> 12:25.310
Just checkin' in on you again.

12:27.046 --> 12:30.982
(sigh) look at you, dozin'
so peaceful-like.

12:30.984 --> 12:34.018
Here I am, checkin' up on ya
every five seconds.

12:34.020 --> 12:35.887
And you're totally fine.

12:35.889 --> 12:38.957
Maybe you don't need me
frettin' over you all the time.

12:38.959 --> 12:42.293
Wow! Apple bloom will be
so glad to hear that!

12:42.295 --> 12:43.762
Huh?

12:43.764 --> 12:45.163
Scootaloo?

12:45.165 --> 12:46.931
Uh, no.

12:48.367 --> 12:49.367
Sweetie belle?

12:49.369 --> 12:51.436
But where's apple bloom?

12:51.438 --> 12:52.470
She's not here!

12:53.773 --> 12:54.906
<i>She could be anywhere!</i>

12:54.908 --> 12:59.077
<i>She could be lost, cold,</i>
<i>hungry, itchy, stuffed up,</i>

12:59.079 --> 13:00.545
<i>Needin' to go to the bathroom!</i>

13:00.547 --> 13:03.047
Don't worry. We know
exactly where she is.

13:03.049 --> 13:05.116
Yeah. She's making
your pie delivery.

13:06.252 --> 13:07.952
What? No!

13:07.954 --> 13:10.889
Didn't she hear how difficult
and dangerous it was?

13:10.891 --> 13:12.090
<i>(horrified gasp)</i>

13:12.092 --> 13:15.193
I may never see my
little sister again!

13:19.565 --> 13:23.168
Ok, rarity's on her way here
to look after you two.

13:23.170 --> 13:26.237
Now tell me, did apple bloom at
least bring flame-proof boots?

13:27.873 --> 13:29.040
A lion tamer's chair?

13:30.242 --> 13:31.810
A snake-charming flute?

13:32.912 --> 13:34.112
A hunk of ricotta?

13:35.281 --> 13:36.214
<i>(gasp)</i>

13:38.852 --> 13:42.854
Maybe there's still time to
catch her before she gets there.

13:42.856 --> 13:44.189
<i>When did she leave?</i>

13:44.191 --> 13:45.857
It must have been hours ago.

13:47.026 --> 13:47.992
Oh no!

13:50.596 --> 13:53.531
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

13:53.533 --> 14:03.842
♪

14:03.844 --> 14:18.256
♪

14:18.258 --> 14:21.059
I can't see a darn
thing in this swamp.

14:21.061 --> 14:22.026
Ah!

14:24.163 --> 14:25.096
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:25.098 --> 14:26.064
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:26.066 --> 14:27.465
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:27.467 --> 14:29.934
Well, now at least I can see.

14:32.238 --> 14:33.204
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:34.607 --> 14:38.142
<i>(low growl)</i>

14:38.144 --> 14:39.244
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:48.187 --> 14:49.254
(whoosh)

14:49.889 --> 14:50.521
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:56.528 --> 14:59.297
I'd stay where you are.

14:59.299 --> 15:02.333
This is the only safe
spot around here.

15:02.335 --> 15:06.404
It don't look
so safe to me.

15:06.406 --> 15:09.574
Oh, we just mean
from the flames.

15:09.576 --> 15:12.377
Yeah, not from us.

15:12.379 --> 15:14.245
What was that?

15:14.247 --> 15:17.448
Can you guys sssspeak up?

15:17.450 --> 15:23.221
I was about to tell our guest
how we haven't eaten in days.

15:23.223 --> 15:26.291
My sisters and I can never
agree on what to eat!

15:26.293 --> 15:27.592
<i>(hiss)</i>

15:27.594 --> 15:29.961
Except pie.

15:34.133 --> 15:37.969
Well, unfortunately, I got to
get these pies to a town

15:37.971 --> 15:40.071
<i>On the other side of</i>
<i>the swamp. So uh...</i>

15:40.073 --> 15:43.141
Oh, you don't have
to worry about that.

15:43.143 --> 15:47.011
Yeah, you don't have to
worry about anything anymore.

15:47.013 --> 15:49.480
Because we're gonna
have our apple pie

15:49.482 --> 15:53.251
With a sssside
of filly filet!

15:53.253 --> 15:54.585
You don't say.

15:54.587 --> 15:56.387
<i>(nervous laugh)</i>

15:56.389 --> 16:02.126
<i>(growling/bleating/hissing)</i>

16:03.629 --> 16:06.064
Now sisters, on three.

16:06.066 --> 16:06.664
One.

16:08.567 --> 16:09.400
Two!

16:11.070 --> 16:12.503
<i>(hiss)</i>

16:12.505 --> 16:13.371
Three!

16:15.240 --> 16:25.316
<i>(clattering hooves)</i>

16:25.318 --> 16:26.184
<i>(skid)</i>

16:26.186 --> 16:27.218
No!

16:29.254 --> 16:31.456
Where do you think you're going?

16:33.058 --> 16:36.294
<i>(threatening growls)</i>

16:36.296 --> 16:37.562
<i>(whoosh)</i>

16:39.598 --> 16:42.066
<i>(hiss)</i>

16:42.068 --> 16:42.734
<i>(frightened shout)</i>

16:43.769 --> 16:46.004
<i>(panicked whimpers)</i>

16:46.006 --> 16:46.738
Oomph!

16:48.540 --> 16:50.408
<i>(panting)</i>

16:50.410 --> 16:57.648
<i>(grunts)</i>

17:05.090 --> 17:06.424
<i>(whoosh)</i>

17:06.426 --> 17:14.699
<i>♪</i>

17:14.701 --> 17:19.437
<i>(growl/bleat/hiss)</i>

17:19.439 --> 17:21.806
Where are the pies?

17:21.808 --> 17:23.474
They're not back here.

17:23.476 --> 17:25.143
This is your fault!

17:25.145 --> 17:28.479
You think you've always
got to be in charge.

17:28.481 --> 17:30.081
You're lucky, you know.

17:30.083 --> 17:32.417
You've got no idea what it's
like to have a sister

17:32.419 --> 17:34.552
<i>Constantly looking</i>
<i>over your shoulder.</i>

17:34.554 --> 17:36.421
Uh, actually...

17:36.423 --> 17:39.157
Let's try listening
to me for a change.

17:39.159 --> 17:41.759
And I say: If
there are no pies,

17:41.761 --> 17:45.063
Let's settle for
the filly filet.

17:45.065 --> 17:46.697
(hiss)

17:46.699 --> 17:50.735
Any last words?

17:50.737 --> 17:52.703
I really wish my
sister were here!

17:52.705 --> 17:54.138
<i>(hiss)</i>

17:54.140 --> 17:56.441
<i>Hang on, apple bloom!</i>
<i>I'm a'comin'!</i>

18:00.646 --> 18:01.712
<i>Together: Get her!</i>

18:01.714 --> 18:04.816
Hey, I thought I
was in charge now!

18:04.818 --> 18:09.854
♪

18:09.856 --> 18:11.389
<i>(growl)</i>

18:21.166 --> 18:23.234
<i>(hiss)</i>

18:23.236 --> 18:24.702
<i>(thud)</i>

18:24.704 --> 18:26.104
<i>(growl)</i>

18:28.373 --> 18:31.275
<i>(roar)</i>

18:34.179 --> 18:37.782
<i>(gasping)</i>

18:37.784 --> 18:38.816
<i>(crunch)</i>

18:40.719 --> 18:42.220
Howdy!

18:46.625 --> 18:47.558
<i>(snap)</i>

18:50.562 --> 18:51.496
<i>(smash)</i>

18:52.364 --> 18:57.635
<i>(struggling grunts)</i>

19:01.473 --> 19:02.707
<i>(snarl)</i>

19:07.913 --> 19:10.281
Mmmm. Ricotta!

19:10.283 --> 19:13.151
<i>(groans)</i>

19:13.685 --> 19:14.519
Let's go!

19:17.256 --> 19:18.422
<i>(whoosh)</i>

19:18.424 --> 19:19.390
<i>(whoosh)</i>

19:19.392 --> 19:20.158
<i>(whoosh)</i>

19:20.160 --> 19:21.392
<i>(whoosh)</i>

19:24.296 --> 19:25.296
Are you ok?

19:26.465 --> 19:27.532
Thanks to you.

19:29.434 --> 19:32.270
I told ya ya need your big
sister looking after you!

19:32.272 --> 19:34.605
I'm just glad this
wasn't a whole lot worse.

19:34.607 --> 19:37.441
I mean, sure, we lost the
cart and all the pies,

19:37.443 --> 19:38.576
But at least you're--

19:43.182 --> 19:45.483
The cart! And all the pies!

19:45.485 --> 19:48.719
You actually got them all
the up way here, in the dark,

19:48.721 --> 19:51.956
Through the flame geyser
swamp, past that monster?

19:53.825 --> 19:55.560
By yourself?

19:55.562 --> 19:57.728
Well... Yeah.

19:57.730 --> 20:02.733
Wow. That's mighty
impressive.

20:02.735 --> 20:05.436
Anypony who can do
that on her own, well,

20:05.438 --> 20:08.339
She don't need somepony
like me babying her.

20:13.645 --> 20:18.349
<i>♪ (zydeco accordion)</i>

20:18.351 --> 20:19.483
<i>(splash)</i>

20:19.485 --> 20:22.486
Mmmmm!
Andouille!

20:22.488 --> 20:26.424
(cajun accent)
dis pie's even tastier den ma
mama's swamp-water casserole!

20:26.426 --> 20:30.428
<i>(cheers)</i>

20:30.430 --> 20:32.830
Aw, now, mama,
don't be like dat!

20:32.832 --> 20:35.967
<i>(excited chatter)</i>

20:37.836 --> 20:40.705
Just remember, you fellas
wouldn't be enjoyin' these pies

20:40.707 --> 20:42.940
If it weren't for my sister.

20:42.942 --> 20:45.009
And my sister!

20:45.011 --> 20:46.544
But this don't change the fact

20:46.546 --> 20:48.546
That trying to make this
delivery on your own

20:48.548 --> 20:50.448
Was a plumb crazy
thing to do.

20:50.450 --> 20:52.416
I know.

20:52.418 --> 20:56.454
I bet granny smith grounds you
for a month for sneakin' out!

20:56.456 --> 20:59.423
And if big mac, granny smith
and I ever have to be away

20:59.425 --> 21:00.658
For the day again...

21:02.027 --> 21:04.428
I would totally trust
you to stay home

21:04.430 --> 21:07.265
And take care of
things on your own.

21:07.267 --> 21:11.402
I guess I did get a little
carried away watchin' over ya,

21:11.404 --> 21:13.437
And if ya hadn't snuck
out like you did,

21:13.439 --> 21:15.539
Maybe I wouldn't have
figured that out.

21:15.541 --> 21:18.643
Yes! Now  <u>that</u> is the kind
of looking out for me

21:18.645 --> 21:21.312
I can definitely appreciate!

21:21.314 --> 21:22.947
So we're good?

21:22.949 --> 21:25.816
Little sister,
we're always good.

21:25.818 --> 21:28.653
♪
